snippet.title: Ranita Fishing Gameplay Clips
snippet.description: Ranita Fishing is about a little frog on a quest for their grandpa, collecting fish and helping friends along the way. "We are a group of friends from México that decided to work together on a little game for fun. if you are a publisher... we really wanna make the whole game!" https://fayer.itch.io/ranita #indiegames #freegames #videogames
